excel_file <- "WydatkiDane.xlsx"

sheet_name1 <- "WydatkiAll"
sheet_name2 <- "WydatkiDziay"
sheet_name3 <- "Czci1"
sheet_name4 <- "Czci2"
sheet_name5 <- "Fundusze"
sheet_name6 <- "BudetyDziay"
sheet_name7 <- "BudetyTop"
sheet_name8 <- "ZusDziay"
sheet_name9 <- "ZusTop"
sheet_name10 <- "ZabezpieczeniaTop"
sheet_name11 <- "KrusTop"
sheet_name12 <- "InneTop"
sheet_name13 <- "PracaTop"
sheet_name14 <- "FUSfundusze"
sheet_name15 <- "RentTop"
sheet_name16 <- "ChorobTop"
sheet_name17 <- "WypadTop"
sheet_name18 <- "EmeRenTop"
sheet_name19 <- "FundPracTop"
sheet_name20 <- "FS"

WydatkiAll <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name1, col_names = TRUE)
WydatkiDziay <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name2, col_names = TRUE)
Czci1 <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name3, col_names = TRUE)
Czci2 <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name4, col_names = TRUE)
Fundusze <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name5, col_names = TRUE)
BudetyDziay <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name6, col_names = TRUE)
BudetyTop <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name7, col_names = TRUE)
ZusDziay <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name8, col_names = TRUE)
ZusTop <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name9, col_names = TRUE)
ZabezpieczeniaTop <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name10, col_names = TRUE)
KrusTop <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name11, col_names = TRUE)
InneTop <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name12, col_names = TRUE)
PracaTop <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name13, col_names = TRUE)
FUSfundusze <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name14, col_names = TRUE)
RentTop <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name15, col_names = TRUE)
ChorobTop <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name16, col_names = TRUE)
WypadTop <- read_excel(excel_file, sheet = sheet_name17, col_names = TRUE)

WydatkiAllWykres

WydatkiAllWykres <- ggplot(WydatkiAll, aes(x = Rok)) +
  geom_col(aes(y = `Wydatki budetowe oglnie`, fill = "Wydatki budetowe oglnie"), show.legend = TRUE) +
  geom_col(aes(y = `Wydatki na polityk spoeczn`, fill = "Wydatki na polityk spoeczn"), show.legend = TRUE) +
  scale_y_continuous(
   breaks = seq(0, 550, by = 50),
    limits = c(0, 550),
    expand = c(0, 100)) +
  theme_stata() +
  scale_fill_stata() +
  scale_color_stata() +
  
  geom_text(aes(y = `Wydatki budetowe oglnie` + (0.035 * max(`Wydatki budetowe oglnie`)), label = round(`Wydatki budetowe oglnie`, 1)), size = 3, color = "black") +
  geom_text(aes(y = `Wydatki na polityk spoeczn` - (0.1 * max(`Wydatki na polityk spoeczn`)), label = round(`Wydatki na polityk spoeczn`, 1)), size = 3, color = "black") +
   theme(legend.position = "bottom") +
  
  labs(
    x = "Rok",
    y = "Wydatki w mld z",
    fill = "Rodzaj wydatkw"
  )

WydatkiDziayWykres <- ggplot(WydatkiDziay, aes(x = Rok)) +

  geom_line(aes(y = `Obowizkowe ubezpieczenia spoeczne`, group = 1, color = "Obowizkowe ubezpieczenia spoeczne"), show.legend = TRUE, size = 1.5, linetype = "solid") +
  geom_point(aes(y = `Obowizkowe ubezpieczenia spoeczne`, color = "Obowizkowe ubezpieczenia spoeczne", shape = "Obowizkowe ubezpieczenia spoeczne"), size = 3) +

geom_text_repel(aes(y = `Rodzina`, label = round(`Rodzina`, 2)), size = 3, color = "black") +

  labs(
    x = "Rok",

    color = "Dzia budetowy",
    shape = "Dzia budetowy"
  )
